  <!-- Introducción de la actividad -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="narrative-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>The purpose of this activity is for students to apply understandings from previous lessons to create a picture graph with a scale of 2 from the categorical data they gathered. Students are guided to use a scale of 2 but can choose their own symbol. Depending on the data, students may need to use a half symbol in order to represent an odd number of students choosing a specific method of travel. This idea is discussed in the synthesis.</p>
<p>Students will use their scaled picture graphs again in the next lesson.</p>
  </paragraphs>


